00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:56,400
Dengan niat seperti apa kau
masuk ke Keluarga Rong?

217
00:14:58,119 --> 00:14:59,700
Apakah kau tahu
kebenaran di balik ini…

218
00:15:02,039 --> 00:15:06,119
…atau itu sebabnya kau
mendorongku pergi dengan tegas?

219
00:15:24,799 --> 00:15:25,479
Halo.

220
00:15:26,799 --> 00:15:27,880
Lakukan sesuatu untukku.

221
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,119
Nona, mau keluar?

222
00:15:33,159 --> 00:15:33,670
Iya.

223
00:15:33,679 --> 00:15:35,520
(Aula Anji)

224
00:15:45,119 --> 00:15:46,200
Ikuti dia.

225
00:15:47,559 --> 00:15:48,520
Silakan duduk.

226
00:15:48,799 --> 00:15:50,039
Cepat.

227
00:16:01,479 --> 00:16:02,440
Terima kasih.

228
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:17,350
(Shudeli)

229
00:16:36,479 --> 00:16:37,080
Halo.

230
00:16:37,599 --> 00:16:38,840
Tuan Muda Pertama Rong.

231
00:16:39,039 --> 00:16:40,840
Jika aku tidak meneleponmu,…

232
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:43,100
